---
import site from '@/lib/site'
---

<section class="section s5-steps">
  <div class="container container--narrow">

    <div class="s5-steps__intro">
      <h2 class="s5-steps__heading">What To Expect During Your 60-Minute Dermaplaning Facial Experience</h2>
      <p class="s5-steps__sub">Every step is designed for your comfort and results. Here's exactly what happens during your session at Menon Medispa in Millburn, NJ.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="s5-steps__list">

      <div class="s5-steps__item">
        <p class="s5-steps__item-title"><strong>Step 1: Consultation &amp; Skin Analysis (5-10 minutes)</strong></p>
        <p class="s5-steps__item-desc">Your esthetician will assess your skin type, discuss any concerns, and confirm dermaplaning is the right treatment for your complexion that day.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="s5-steps__item">
        <p class="s5-steps__item-title"><strong>Step 2: Deep Cleansing &amp; Preparation (10-15 minutes)</strong></p>
        <p class="s5-steps__item-desc">We use the Corthe Dermo Cleansing Foam to remove makeup, oil, and impurities and prepare your skin for dermaplaning. Your skin is then toned and prepped for the exfoliation step.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="s5-steps__item">
        <p class="s5-steps__item-title"><strong>Step 3: Professional Dermaplaning (15-20 minutes)</strong></p>
        <p class="s5-steps__item-desc">Using a sterile surgical blade held at a precise 45-degree angle, your esthetician gently glides across the skin to remove dead skin cells and fine vellus hair. The process is virtually painless.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="s5-steps__item">
        <p class="s5-steps__item-title"><strong>Step 4: Serum &amp; Moisturizer Application (10-15 minutes)</strong></p>
        <p class="s5-steps__item-desc">With your skin freshly exfoliated, we apply targeted serums and a hydrating moisturizer to lock in results. Your session finishes with a broad-spectrum SPF to protect your newly revealed skin.</p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="s5-steps__cta">
      <a href={site.calcomUrl} class="btn btn--primary btn--lg">Schedule Now</a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .s5-steps__intro {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .s5-steps__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h2);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-sm);
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .s5-steps__sub {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .s5-steps__list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .s5-steps__item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .s5-steps__item-title {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .s5-steps__item-desc {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .s5-steps__cta {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: var(--space-lg);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .s5-steps__cta .btn {
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
    }
  }
</style>
